General.Name: Triductor Technology (Suzhou) Inc.
General.Description: Triductor Technology (Suzhou) Inc., a semiconductor company, designs and provides mixed-signal integrated circuits, and related hardware and software applications. It also offers power line communication chipsets, carrier access network chipsets, and chip layout design services, as well as related application solutions and other technical services. In addition, the company communication algorithms and system software, and digital circuit design and analog design services. The company was founded in 2005 and is based in Suzhou, China.
